scenes = [
    {
        "voiceover": "You are exactly one emotional decision away from destroying months of hard work. I know this, because right now, you are trying to convince yourself that the very next trade is the one that fixes everything. It isn't. It's the one that breaks you completely.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The lime green stick figure standing perfectly still on a sheet of glass that has a massive, terrifying spiderweb crack spreading under his feet. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy red: 'ONE MISTAKE'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "We need to talk about the most dangerous lie in the entire trading industry. It’s that little whisper in your ear after you take a painful loss, telling you that if you just size up and go heavy this one time, you can wipe the slate clean and get it all back.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The lime green stick figure looking distressed while a tiny, dark red stick figure with devil horns stands on his shoulder, whispering into his ear. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy black: 'THE LIE'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "But let me ask you a very serious question. Be honest with yourself. When was the last time revenge trading actually worked out for you? When was the last time you traded out of pure, blind anger, and the market actually rewarded your lack of discipline?",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The lime green stick figure holding a giant magnifying glass, looking at a completely blank, empty accounting ledger book. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy red: 'ZERO'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "The harsh reality is this: the exact moment you try to force the market to pay you back for a loss, you have completely stopped trading. You have officially crossed the line from a professional risk manager into a degenerate gambler.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The lime green stick figure sitting mindlessly in front of a giant casino slot machine that has glowing red charts on its spinning wheels. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy red: 'THE CASINO'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "You stop looking for high-probability setups. You stop checking your daily bias. You just stare at the flickering candles, desperately pulling the lever of the slot machine, hoping the algorithm will magically grant you a jackpot to heal your ego.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The stick figure frantically pulling a heavy metal lever attached to a computer monitor, with dollar signs spinning wildly in his eyes. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy black: 'DESPERATION'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "And because you are trading on pure emotion, you enter a terrible position. Deep down, in your gut, you know the trade is completely invalid. But your finger clicks the mouse anyway, because the pain of doing nothing feels worse than the risk of losing.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The stick figure holding a computer mouse, while his own brain literally reaches out with hands to try and stop his finger from clicking. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy red: 'NO CONTROL'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "Immediately, the position goes against you. You are instantly in a massive drawdown. Your heart is pounding against your ribs, your palms are sweating, and you are completely paralyzed by the fear of blowing your account.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The stick figure completely frozen in a block of solid ice, sweating drops of water, while a giant red arrow points straight down beside him. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy black: 'PARALYZED'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "This is the turning point where accounts go to die. Instead of taking the loss like a professional and protecting your capital, you commit the ultimate cardinal sin. You reach out, click your stop loss, and you drag it further away.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The stick figure erasing a protective wall with an eraser, deliberately exposing himself to a raging storm of red arrows. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy red: 'THE SIN'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "You tell yourself you are just giving the trade 'room to breathe.' But that is just another lie. You aren't giving the trade room to breathe; you are actively suffocating your own trading account because your ego refuses to admit it was wrong.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The lime green stick figure stubbornly putting a crown on his own head while his entire desk is burning down around him. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy black: 'EGO'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "The market is a cold, calculating machine. It does not care about your rent, it does not care about your dreams, and it certainly does not care about your hopes. It simply moves to areas of liquidity, crushing anyone who stands in the way without a plan.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. A giant, faceless bulldozer pushing a massive pile of dead red stick figures off a cliff, completely indifferent. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy black: 'RUTHLESS'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "The massive red candle forms. It rips through your account equity like a chainsaw. Your screen freezes, the broker notification pops up, and it is over. You have officially blown the account. Again.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. A giant, heavy steel vault door slamming violently shut, with a massive red padlock locking the stick figure out of his own account. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy red: 'LOCKED OUT'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "Then comes the silence. You sit alone in your room, staring at a red screen. The anger fades, replaced by a hollow, sickening feeling of heavy regret in your stomach. You knew exactly what you were supposed to do, and you failed to do it.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The stick figure sitting alone on the floor in a vast, empty white space, hugging his knees, looking completely drained. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy black: 'THE SILENCE'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "Listen to me very carefully. The market did not take your money today. The algorithm did not hunt you down. You took your own money, put it on a silver platter, and voluntarily handed it to a more disciplined trader.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The lime green stick figure kneeling down and politely handing a silver tray full of gold coins to a shadowy, calm figure. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy red: 'YOU GAVE IT AWAY'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "If you want to survive in this industry, you have to fundamentally change what you consider a 'win'. Making money is not a win. Following your trading plan with absolute, robotic precision—that is the only true win.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The lime green stick figure completely ignoring a pile of cash, proudly holding up a piece of paper with a green checkmark on it. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy lime green: 'THE REAL WIN'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "Before you ever click the buy or sell button, you must completely and totally accept the risk. You must mentally write that money off as gone. If you cannot accept the risk, you have absolutely no business being in the trade.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The stick figure calmly signing a heavy legal contract with a feather pen, while holding a bag of money. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy black: 'ACCEPTANCE'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "Profitable trading is not exciting. It is not an action movie. It is an incredibly boring, highly repetitive routine of waiting for your exact edge to appear, executing it flawlessly, and doing nothing else.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The lime green stick figure wearing a factory worker uniform, rhythmically stamping a single piece of paper on a massive conveyor belt. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy lime green: 'THE ROUTINE'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "When you take a normal, planned loss, you don't fight back. You don't seek revenge. You close your laptop, you stand up from your desk, and you walk away. Your mental capital is infinitely more valuable than your financial capital.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The lime green stick figure firmly slamming his laptop shut, turning his back, and confidently walking away toward an open door. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy black: 'WALK AWAY'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "Your only job in this market is survival. If you can survive the drawdown periods without doing something incredibly stupid, the winning streaks will naturally take care of themselves. Protect your chips so you can play tomorrow.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The lime green stick figure hiding safely inside a heavy steel bunker, while a chaotic storm of red arrows rains down outside. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy lime green: 'SURVIVAL'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "Stop looking for the holy grail indicator. Stop jumping from strategy to strategy. The holy grail is not on your charts; it is inside your head. It is the ability to master your own impulses.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. The lime green stick figure tapping his own forehead with his index finger, while a glowing lock and key appear inside his brain. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy lime green: 'THE HOLY GRAIL'."
    },
    {
        "voiceover": "You have the power to break this destructive cycle today. Forgive yourself for the blown accounts, burn your ego to the ground, and commit to being the disciplined, robotic trader you are meant to be.",
        "prompt": "Create a minimalist clean hand-drawn cartoon illustration with thick bold black ink outlines on a pure solid white background. A powerful, heroic stick figure rising out of a pile of ashes, glowing with a calm, lime green aura. Massive, thick, bold, hand-drawn felt-tip marker font in heavy lime green: 'REBIRTH'."
    }
]